text: Erest on endeburgh and so on cathole.

Þanne on crawenburgh þanne on doddam mere þanen on Smalewey þanen os puddokesburghe þanne on Whiteston þanne on Stremeston þanne on þe White weye þane on þe redeslo þanne on rigte Weye þanne on egelferdeston þanne on Wulvesburghe þanne on Wringput.
Þanne on davidisdich þanne eft on endeburgh.
